      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Significant technical maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a recent valve shim adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate fatigue, a critical upgrade for this platform. It sits on staggered Style 67 alloys wrapped in high-performance compound tires, maintaining the original suspension geometry for authentic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. This is a mechanically sound specimen optimized for performance and longevity.",
